SELECT pm.id, pm.property_type, pm.property_address, pm.market_value, pa.trend_category FROM property_market_data pm INNER JOIN property_trend_analysis pa ON pm.id = pa.property_id WHERE pa.trend_date >= '2022-01-01' ORDER BY pa.trend_date DESC, market_value DESC;
